## Browser compatibility

- This project uses the [File System Access API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_System_Access_API), which at the moment is only available in Chromium‑based desktop browsers and only in secure contexts (`https://` or `http://localhost`).[web:23][web:45]
- If you need support for Firefox/Safari, you would have to:
  - Fall back to classic `<input type="file" webkitdirectory>` or multiple file pickers.
  - Replace `showDirectoryPicker` + directory handles with a different approach.

